<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.4">
<l>mainnampu vēlkaṇnal lāḷmuṉṉam peṟṟa vaḷaivaṇṇa naṉmā mēṉi</l>
<l>taṉnam pinampi yumiṅku vaḷarnta tavaṉi vaicey  taṟiyāṉ</l>
<l>poynnampi puḷḷuvaṉ kaḷvam potiyaṟai pōkiṉṟa vāta vaḻntiṭ</l>
<l>ṭinnampi nampiyā vāycciyark kuyvillai yeṉceykē ṉeṉcey kēṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord’s lord with a fine, large body the color of a conch</l>
<l rend="indent">whom the fine lady, with lance[-like] eyes that deserve kohl,</l>
<l>Previously begot, [his] upbringing was also here;</l>
<l rend="indent">he does not think of doing these things.</l>
<l>The way this lord of lies, this deceiver,</l>
<l rend="indent">this storehouse of thievery goes creeping!</l>
<l>Since this lord is lord, there is no escape for the herder women!</l>
<l rend="indent">What do I do? What do I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
